-- Itaú says loan book strategy key to offsetting Brazil slowdown
-- By Guillermo Parra-Bernal and Aluísio Alves
-- Wed Apr 30, 2014 09:38AM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, April 30 (Reuters) - Itaú Unibanco Holding SA's <ITUB4.SA> strategy to increase loan disbursements on the least-risky segments is necessary to help Brazil's largest bank by market value weather the impact of a slowing economy, a senior executive said on Wednesday.

